# Workers Static Assets handles the SPA fallback automatically via
# `not_found_handling: "single-page-application"` in wrangler.jsonc, so
# no explicit /* → /index.html rule is needed.
#
# External proxy rewrites (e.g. /sitemap.xml → Supabase) are not
# supported here; the sitemap is exposed directly at its Supabase URL
# and referenced from robots.txt.
